'Serre' may refer to:

* Serre (surname)
* Serre (grape), a red Italian wine grape
* Serre Chevalier, a major French ski resort in the southern part of the Alps
* Serre (river), a tributary of the Oise in France
* Serre, Campania, a town and comune in the province of Salerno in the Campania
  region of south-western Italy
* Serre Calabresi, a mountain and hill area of Calabria, Italy
* a greenhouse in French, like in the Jardin Serre de la Madone park in Menton,
  Alpes-Maritimes, Provence-Alpes-Côte d'Azur, France
